cukta di'usro

Posted on February 24, 2015 by Ross

fanva zoi sy La Biblioteca sy
fi’e la’o gy Community gy

ma stuzi lo cukta di’usro
se cmene zo bog ne lo jukni salta misro
salta misro i skuro i cukta di’usro lonu mutce tebykre i gerku i cidro
i cidro tebykre i pelkre i zargu
i loi prije cu pluta i loi birje cu xamgu
xamgu djedi i nelci lekypatlu
i kanba krebasti tebykre la .lusi.lu.

Where is the library?
My name is Bone, the spider-salad Egyptian
Salad Egyptian, groove, library of extreme moustaches, dog, hydrogen
Hydrogen beard, blond, arse.
Wisdom is the route, beer is good.
Good day, like-able cold potatoes.
Goat-wig mustache of Lucy Lu
